---

<div class="space-y-6">
    <div class="text-primary mb-5 text-sm font-bold uppercase">Projects</div>
    <h2 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-bold">Selected work</h2>
    <p>A few examples of the kind of systems I build:</p>
    <div class="flex gap-3">
        <div class="flex-2/3 space-y-3 p-3">
            <div class="border-border space-y-2 border-b pb-3">
                <h3 class="font-semibold">Listegy</h3>
                <p>
                    AI-assisted e-commerce listing workflow turned into
                    structured software.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="border-border space-y-2 border-b pb-3">
                <h3 class="font-semibold">Expensior</h3>
                <p>
                    Internal expense and payment workflow replacing
                    spreadsheet-heavy tracking.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-2 pb-3">
                <h3 class="font-semibold">Logistics Website</h3>
                <p>
                    Clean static business website without WordPress/plugin
                    overhead.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="border-border flex-1/3 space-y-3 border-l p-6">
            <h4 class="font-bold">
                Have a messy workflow that should become a real tool?
            </h4>
            <p>
                Or need a simple website without WordPress overhead? Bring the
                problem. I’ll help you decide the cleanest next step.
            </p>

            <div class="space-x-3">
                <button
                    class="text-background bg-primary hover:bg-primary/80 hover:text-text/90 rounded px-3 py-2 text-lg font-semibold transition"
                >
                    Book a call
                </button>

                <button
                    class="text-text bg-background border-border hover:bg-text/20 rounded border px-3 py-2 text-lg transition"
                >
                    See selected work
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
